"AW-NB037H" is printed on the PCB.
Comes with a half-height to full-height adapter. AR9002WB-1NGCD chipset (AR9285+AR3011) The FCC ID is that of the Asus EEE PC X101 and is not a Habey or AzureWave submission of this device. It is there for convenience's sake to link the device to the OEM model. The OUI may be (or include) 48:5D:60. [[Category:English Documentation]]
